    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Forgot to mention that I used fresh raspberries, for those wondering if that&#8217;s OK: a big yes! We used berries we had picked ourselves, that were on their way out and breaking down a bit &#8212; and still the cake was blissful!</p>
    </div>

